crypto: hisilicon - PASID fixed on Kunpeng 930

Enable PASID by setting 'sqc' and 'cqc' pasid bits
per queue in Kunpeng 930.

For Kunpeng 920, PASID is effective for all queues once set
in SVA scenarios.

